Phase 1: Getting the postgreSQL DB to work				June 6th - 1st July \
\
Goal of Phase 1: \
	The Goal of Phase 1 is that the structure of the postgreSQL implementation of the political configuration data works such that  \
		(i)	the data provided matches the conceptual/theoretical definitions; \
		(ii)	the provision of data is consistent and efficient, i.e., updating data requires the least effort in terms of user-input and has the biggest and impact through automatization; \
		(iii)	the structure of the DB is only as complex as necessary and well-documented, in order to \
			(a) minimize the effort required for maintenance, and\
			(b) allow (future) employees to understand its workings as fast as possible\
	Overall, the structure of the posgreSQL DB should make sure that the public configuration view(s) unambiguously re-present the conceptual definition of political configurations \
\
