Phase 2: Updating data in the PCDB						July 4th - July 29th\
\
Goal of Phase 2:\
	The Goal of Phase 2 is that multiple user can easily update (Insert/Delete/Update) data in the PCDB Base tables, ideally with a minimum amount of knowledge of SQL necessary. \
	An intuitive procedure, for instance, would not require more than loading data gathered in a .csv-file into the respective table, such that updates/inserts are executed automatically.\
	Importantly, achieving this goal will involve automatization of updating procedures, and of version control and back-up procedures, in order to reduce the risk of fatal (i.e., irreversible) errors when changing data in the PCDB.\
	In terms of data, throughout Phase 2 extensive consistency checks and reviewing should produce a number of .csv-file that list necessary updates on the data in the PCDB.\
